io.spine.tools.compiler.annotation

Class Annotator

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.tools.compiler.annotation.Annotator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OptionAnnotator

    public abstract class Annotator
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract base class for the annotators of the generated Java sources.

    Annotator inserts a reference to the specified annotation to the pre-configured spots of the Java files, generated basing on Protobuf definitions.

        protected final void addAnnotation(org.jboss.forge.roaster.model.source.AnnotationTargetSource<?,?> source)
        Adds a fully qualified annotation to the AnnotationTargetSource.

        If the specified source already has the annotation, does nothing to avoid annotation duplication and a compilation error as a result.

        Parameters:
